text: Reminder: There are lots of great ways to stay connected with what’s happening in HubSpot development. To be made aware of any changes that affect developers we recommend <https://developers.HubSpot.com/changelog|subscribing to our developer changelog>. We post announcements about new developer facing functionality as well as communicate from there if we need to make <https://developers.HubSpot.com/docs/breaking-change-definition|breaking changes>.

Introducing the HubSpot Template Marketplace, including themes and modules August 2022 Developer Updates Today, July 12th 2023, HubSpot announced a redesigned template marketplace, now listing standalone modules, in addition to themes. Read more about it on our changelog. :rolled_up_newspaper: View on Changelog button Want to join HubSpot’s Template Marketplace and sell your themes or modules? Learn more about becoming a template provider and building for the template marketplace by visiting: <https://www.HubSpot.com/template-providers>
